name: Red Runtz
description: Red Runtz is a weed strain bred by Exotic Genetix. Red Runtz crosses the super-popular Runtz strain to the more rare and soda-flavored Red Pop. Exotic Genetix breeds for maximum THC and crazy frost. This strain should have Runtz's mix of fruity, creamy, berry terps with Red Pop's red strawberry soda pop terp.
